NOTE: before running protractor (e2e) tests, you must issue a command:
npm run update-webdriver

Testing client-side:
grunt test:client
Runs:
  •	'clean:server',
    -- Empties .tmp folder
  •	'env:all',
    -- Sets server environment for testing on localhost:9000 
  •	'injector:sass', 
    -- Injects component scss into app.scss
    -- May be part of ‘watch’ process?
  •	'concurrent:test',
    -- Runs the sass tests in parallel (to speed up build process)
    -- Part of grunt init.config
  •	'injector',
    -- Injects application script files into index.html
  •	'autoprefixer',
    -- “Add vendor prefixed styles”
    -- Part of grunt init.config, and might be part of watch task
  •	'karma'
    -- Runs karma test
    -- Config file is at ‘karma.conf.js’


Testing server-side:
grunt test:server
Runs:
  •	'env:all',
    -- Sets server environment and tests on localhost:9000 (though browser should launch automatically) 
  •	'env:test',
    -- Sets Node server environment for testing on localhost:9000 
  •	 ‘mochaTest’, 
    -- Runs mocha test
    -- src: ‘server/**/*.spec.js’


Testing end-to-end:
grunt test:e2e
Runs:
  •	'clean:server',
    -- Empties .tmp folder
  •	'env:all',
    -- Sets server environment for testing on localhost:9000 
  •	'env:test',
    -- Sets Node server environment for testing on localhost:9000 
  •	'injector:sass', 
    -- Injects component scss into app.scss
    -- May be part of ‘watch’ process?
  •	'concurrent:test',
    -- Runs the sass tests in parallel (to speed up build process)
    -- Part of grunt init.config
  •	'injector',
    -- Injects application script files into index.html
  •	‘wiredep’,
    -- Automatically inject bower components into map.
  •	'autoprefixer',
    -- “Add vendor prefixed styles”
    -- Part of grunt init.config, and might be part of watch task
  •	‘express:dev’
    -- Run script at ‘server/app.js’
  •	'protractor'
    -- Runs protractor test in Chrome
    -- configFile: 'protractor.conf.js'


Test configuration Locations:
Karma:
  •	configFile: karma.conf.js
mochaTest:
  •	reporter: ‘spec’
  •	src: ‘server/**/*.spec.js’
protractor: (runs protractor tests in chrome)
  •	configFile: 'protractor.conf.js'
